**Sum**: \( 2031 + 2027 + 2025 + 1973 + 1974 + 1899 + 1901 + 1999 = 16156 \).

All values use the formula from [2]: for position \((r, c)\), let \( m = \max(r, c) \), \( n = \min(r, c) \), base = \((m-1)^2\); then adjust based on layer parity (odd \( m \): \( +n \); even \( m \): \( +2m - n \)).

